About

What is ArticleSmart you may be asking? It is a simple app, derived from the desire to be able to easily find articles for research purposes. Stemmed from the desire to be eble to find articles for novel research, ArticleSmart allows you to easily find content that can help you find information for a project or simply be up to date on the information that you are curious about.
Enjoy.
